question:
Which option gives the meaning of the word "angry"?
0. {'key': 'A', 'text': 'this something happens at some time; after this time, it is not happening; people can know: it happened (before).'}
1. {'key': 'B', 'text': "something of one kind, not a thing; people can see it; it moves; when someone is near it, this someone's body feels something; if it touches the body, something very bad happens to the body; if it touches things, something very bad can happen to these things"}
2. {'key': 'C', 'text': 'a thing of one kind; people make things of this kind; it is big: people can be inside it; people live inside things of this kind; when much water moves from the sky, it does not touch the people inside'}
3. {'key': 'D', 'text': "this someone thinks like this: 'someone did some bad something before now; I don't want it; I want to do something (because of this)'; because of this, this someone feels something bad."}

A word whose definition is: "this someone thinks like this: 'someone did some bad something before now; I don't want it; I want to do something (because of this)'; because of this, this someone feels something bad.". Which word is it?
0. {'key': 'A', 'text': 'liar'}
1. {'key': 'B', 'text': 'reminder (the made something)'}
2. {'key': 'C', 'text': 'maker of (X is the maker of Y)'}
3. {'key': 'D', 'text': 'angry'}

Which option gives the meaning of the word "bookmark"?
0. {'key': 'A', 'text': 'this something happens at some time; after this time, it is not happening; people can know: it happened (before).'}
1. {'key': 'B', 'text': 'this something is a big something of kind event; because some very good something happened before now, it happens; when it happens, many people are happy; when it happens, many people feel something good.'}
2. {'key': 'C', 'text': 'someone did something; because of this, there is this something. There is another something. This something is words; these words say something about that other something. Because there is this something, this someone can know where that other something is.'}
