3. {'key': 'D', 'text': 'because this someone does many things, many somethings of kind take happen; other people do not want somethings of this kind to happen; this someone does not want other people to see this someone.'}

Which option gives the meaning of the word "visible"?
0. {'key': 'A', 'text': 'this something is words; someone says them to someone else; this someone knows they are not true; this someone says them because this someone wants the other someone to think they are true.'}
1. {'key': 'B', 'text': 'something of one kind; people can know it about a thing when they see this thing; two things can be the same in this way; someone cannot know it about a thing if this someone cannot see; there are many kinds of it'}
